data.description: Introducing a spacious 4-bedroom, 3-full bath home in Riverpark, offering 2,394 square feet of living space on just over squarter-acre lot. Also with cost saving solar panels.This residence features a split floorplan with one bedroom and bath on one side and the remaining bedrooms and baths on the other. Primary bedroom and bath has walk-in closet double sinks shower and garden tub. The open great room floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, with  granite countertops and a large island.  Outside, enjoy a concrete patio. Pavered retaining wall in the backyard. A 3-car garage for the cars and toys!. Small RV parking with electric and water. This home provides both comfort and practicality. Discover the perfect blend of luxury and functionality in this Riverpark gem
